The following Perl modules are required, install them using CPAN :-

Convert::Base64
Convert::Binary::C
Crypt::CBC
Crypt::Cipher::AES
Data::Dumper
Devel::Size
Digest::SHA
FFI::Platypus
FFI::Platypus::Buffer
FFI::Platypus::Memory
IO::Socket::INET
JSON
LWP::UserAgent
Math::BigInt
Net::WebSocket::Server
Protocol::WebSocket::Client
String::HexConvert
Time::HiRes
ZMQ::FFI


